wminc-custom-editnotice-2: Kugaragaza indimi ushobora gukoresha, nyamuneka koresha $1 . urugero: niba ururimi rwawe kavukire ari igifaransa kandi ushobora no kuvuga icyongereza neza, koresha $2 .
wminc-custom-featuredwikis-active: Ibi birakora kandi birashobora kubona urubuga rwabo rwihariye vuba:
wminc-custom-newarticletext-noprefix: Nyamuneka Icyitonderwa: Urimo gukora page idafite [[ $1 | prefix]]
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-3: Urimo gukora page nshya ([[ $1 | ibanziriza]]) yitwa "{{FULLPAGENAME}}".
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-4: Ongeraho kandi imbanzirizamushinga: [[Page title]] Kuri [[Wx/xx/Page title]] na {{Page title}} Kuri {{Wx/xx/Page title}} .
wminc-custom-newarticletext-withprefix-5: Kugirango ukore ibi mu buryo bwikora, ushobora gukoresha [[ $1 | Ongera igikoresho cya prefix]].
wminc-custom-tb-incorrect-title-title: Urimo kugerageza gukora page ifite umutwe utari wo.
wminc-custom-tb-incorrect-title-text: Umutwe birashoboka cyane ko ubura [[ $1 | prefix]] cyangwa uri m'ubundi buryo butari bwo (inyuguti nkuru ziri prefix, gukurikira gukurikira n'ibindi.).! N !! N! Niba waraje hano uvuye k'urundi rupapuro, nyamuneka garuka hanyuma ukosore umurongo, nyuma ukore page yitiriwe neza. Niba ugerageza gukora page itaziguye, nyamuneka kora page ifite izina ryiza.! N !! N! Niba kubw'amahirwe ayo ari yo yose akubuza gukora page,ayo ariyo yose utekereza ko ufite imiterere y'ukuri, nyamuneka [[ $2 | menyesha abayobozi]].
wminc-custom-tb-invalid-code-title: Urimo kugerageza gukora page idafite [[ $1 | ISO 639-1 cyangwa -3 code]].
wminc-custom-tb-invalid-code-text: Iyi code yaba itemewe cyangwa ntabwo ari ururimi rwemewe ku imishinga mishya ya Wikimedia.! N !! N! Niba waraje hano k'urundi rupapuro urwo arirwo rwose, nyamuneka subira inyuma ukosore umurongo hanyuma ukore page yitwa neza.! N !! N! Niba kubw'amahirwe ayo ari yo yose akubuza gukora page, ari yo yose utekereza ko ifite code ya ISO 639-1 cyangwa -3 yemewe cyangwa iri m'ururimi rwemewe, nyamuneka [[ $1 | menyesha abayobozi]].
wminc-custom-tb-space-colon: Kubw'impamvu za tekiniki, umutwe ntushobora gutangirira k'umwanya cyangwa k'umurongo.
gadget-addprefix: Ongeraho prefix: Mu buryo bwikora wongeyeho prefixes kumahuza mugihe ukora page.
wminc-gadget-addprefix-help: Ntugomba gukoresha prefix mugihe uhindura iyi page. Yongeweho mu buryo bwikora iyo utangaje page.
gadget-interwiki: Interwiki: Ongeraho imikorere yo kongeramo no kwerekana imiyoboro y'ururimi kuva kuri Wikidata.
wminc-gadget-iw-add-wikidata: Ongera umurongo w'ibanze w'ibivugwa kuri Wikidata
wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-text: Koresha iyi fomu kugirango wongere interwiki ukoresheje ikintu cya Wikidata. Gusa wandike ID ya Wikidata cyangwa URL kubintu cyangwa ingingo iriho mu rundi rurimi hepfo hanyuma ukande "{{int: wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-gutangaza}}".
wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-replace-text: Ukanze "{{int: wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-gutangaza}}", uzasimbuza amahuza ya interwiki ashaje kuri iyi page hamwe na interwiki ihuza na Wikidata. Ingingo izakoreshwa mu guhitamo ikintu cya Wikidata niyi ikurikira:
wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-replace-editinste: Niba ibyo atari byo, nyamuneka hindura page kugirango ukosore .
wminc-gadget-iw-dialog-learn-more: Menya byinshi ku birebana na Wikidata
wminc-gadget-iw-error-invalid: Indangamuntu ya Wikidata winjiye cyangwa urupapuro rwahujwe ntirubaho, cyangwa page ntabwo ihujwe na Wikidata. Nyamuneka  ongera ugerageze .
tag-gadget-interwiki-description: impinduka zongeraho interwiki ihuza igikoresho cya interwiki.
gadget-settestwikipreference: Ongeraho "Shyiraho ururimi" na "Shyiraho (umushinga uri mu igeragzwa) nk'umushinga wawe w'ikizamini" buto k'uruhande iyo ureba wiki ziri mu igeragezwa.
